# Internal planning docs stay private — except CHANGELOG.md, the public release
# notes the prototo-website pulls via `gh api .../contents/docs/CHANGELOG.md`.
# (Exclude docs/ contents, not the dir itself, so the re-include below works.)
docs/*
!docs/CHANGELOG.md
